{"ok":false,"msg":"Woah there!! This could've been a dangerous script! Always remember to scripts.get_level what you're running: 

 * If its MIDSEC, it can take your GC! 
 * If its LOWSEC, it can take GC, take/delete upgrades and record your own loc!! 
 * If its NULLSEC, it can do whatever a script can do!!! 

Additionally, scripts.get_access_level can tell you if the script is hidden or not. A loc is ALWAYS hidden, and will record your loc on the user's system. For most npcs this is fine as they self-destruct, but players don't!"}
